OL,5, British Airways has been fined $1.1m   
OL,6, (#878,000) by the US government over   
OL,7, claims it failed to pay refunds for    
OL,8, cancelled flights during the pandemic. 
OL,10,FThe US Department of Transportation    
OL,11,Fsaid the airline had not provided      
OL,12,F"timely refunds to passengers" for     
OL,13,Fabandoned or rescheduled flights to and
OL,14,Ffrom the country.                      
OL,16,FIt said it had received more than 1,200
OL,17,Fcomplaints about the airline.          
OL,19,FBA rejected the claims, saying it had  
OL,20,F"acted lawfully at all times".         
